---
title: Easy Cherry-Glazed Beef & Pork Meatballs with Carrot Noodle Salad & Ponzu Sauce
description: Carrot noodles are the most colourful noodles around. They dazzle in this bowl of beef and pork meatballs and
tossed in a ponzu sauce. It’s a standout at the table that will quickly become a favourite.

